snippet.title: The Walking Dead: The Complete First Season
snippet.description:
The Walking Dead: The Complete First Season includes all 5 episodes of the critically acclaimed series, plus special episode '400 Days'.

• Winner of over 90 'Game of the Year' Awards, 

• All five award-winning episodes plus special episode '400 Days'

• Based on Robert Kirkman's award-winning comic book series

• Choice matters: your decisions change the story around you

Website: http://www.telltalegames.com/walkingdead
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/TheWalkingDeadGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/#!/telltalegamestter.com/#!/telltalegames
